00:00:13.213 --> 00:00:17.072
The other side of Shri Ganesha is that,

00:00:17.273 --> 00:00:25.458
if any Rakshasa or evil troubles you
or irritates you,

00:00:25.659 --> 00:00:31.712
He is Ganapati – meaning the King of Ganas,

00:00:31.913 --> 00:00:38.515
He destroys the rakshasas and evil people.
He ruins them. He destroys them completely.

00:00:38.716 --> 00:00:43.904
You don’t have to tell Him anything.
You need not inform.

00:00:44.105 --> 00:00:51.341
The Ganas are with you. They finish
the people who try to trouble you.

00:00:51.542 --> 00:00:56.000
In Sahaja Yoga you remember that you
are completely protected.

00:00:56.201 --> 00:01:01.366
No one can trouble you – only if you are
in Sahaja Yoga.

00:01:01.575 --> 00:01:04.978
They, the Ganas are always around you
in all directions.

00:01:05.179 --> 00:01:10.393
They have come here also.

00:01:12.390 --> 00:01:25.343
They have put the veil of protection on
you, completely covered you.

00:01:25.544 --> 00:01:30.814
You will not face any troubles. Then you
call it miracle.

00:01:31.015 --> 00:01:32.762
“Mother I don’t know how I was saved.

00:01:32.963 --> 00:01:34.450
I don’t know what happened and how
I was suddenly saved”.

00:01:34.651 --> 00:01:40.531
All this is the work of Ganas. When Ganas
do this work,

00:01:40.732 --> 00:01:44.007
then you understand that you really are
a Sahaja Yogi.

00:01:44.208 --> 00:01:46.609
If they don’t do this work for you,

00:01:46.810 --> 00:01:50.398
then you have to understand that you have
not yet become a complete Sahaja Yogi.

00:01:50.599 --> 00:01:53.709
One more thing about the Ganas

00:01:53.910 --> 00:01:57.006
is that they are all the time working
in our body.

00:01:57.207 --> 00:02:03.019
The work that happens outside the body,
is only when you are a Realized soul.

00:02:03.220 --> 00:02:05.653
When your connection is made with God,

00:02:05.854 --> 00:02:09.581
then they look after your body, your money

00:02:09.782 --> 00:02:13.077
and all your things, your kids are all
looked after by them.

00:02:13.278 --> 00:02:17.798
Before that they live inside us
as antibodies.

00:02:17.999 --> 00:02:22.338
And these antibodies are the ones who
protect us from diseases

00:02:22.539 --> 00:02:25.337
and because of them we can fight diseases.

00:02:25.538 --> 00:02:30.664
This chakra in the center heart, here is
a bone called sternum bone.

00:02:30.865 --> 00:02:35.005
Till twelve years the antibodies are
prepared

00:02:35.206 --> 00:02:38.164
and they move around all over the body
and are ready.

00:02:38.365 --> 00:02:43.127
Whenever there is a problem, sternum starts
shaking and as soon as it shakes,

00:02:43.328 --> 00:02:46.318
like there is a remote control, like that
they come to know.

00:02:46.519 --> 00:02:51.925
And the person coming and attacking you,

00:02:52.126 --> 00:02:55.655
or anything attacking or any virus is there

00:02:55.856 --> 00:03:02.156
or any type of disease entering your body,
they fight with them.
